{"tid":197721,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"ASUS notebook 電池老化?","createTime":"2017-04-12T05:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T06:09:17.000Z","uid":86629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec17cd10c0ce555be9b9a8abc9547e253b8b7ef7","tid":197721,"uid":86629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:10:50.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟15年7月就問左部華碩A50LX<br />\n咁一直都插住電用<br />\n呢排學校要用電腦咁我就帶返學校啦<br />\n但係我發現唔插住電用, 個mon較到最暗都係用到一個鐘多D<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我仲要只係開左個word打字同上網做research<br />\n莫講話較到最光 正常亮度都頂唔到幾耐<br />\n所以想請教下係電池問題定咩 點解會咁快冇電<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a6d32108c1c58cd702150d0177da35084999f9","tid":197721,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:38:38.000Z","msg":"上淘佬買啦<br />\n<br />\n幾十蚊排<br />\n<br />\n用一年再買過排新<br />\n<br />\n電池消耗品嚟"},{"pid":"cb965c5b9333df2abe7c8f5209909fe83d928956","tid":197721,"uid":86629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:57:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上淘佬買啦<br />\n<br />\n幾十蚊排<br />\n<br />\n用一年再買過排新<br />\n<br />\n電池消耗品嚟</blockquote><br />\n但我部notebook揾唔到個個電池位?<br />\n可能要拆開佢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對呢方面0認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過就算識換都好 都淘唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 外國撚"},{"pid":"bdee2215d8c86daa7bb1896ddb0a0b258e8e9ed5","tid":197721,"uid":3434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T06:03:01.000Z","msg":"電池位應該背面有個制 一禁就會彈舊電出黎"},{"pid":"66ae9ea73c7cd53e57a5b1a1ff83c11483fb75f9","tid":197721,"uid":86629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T06:05:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電池位應該背面有個制 一禁就會彈舊電出黎</blockquote><br />\n成個底得個出風口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26243ac70a611f31bee6e446cfc5599f80cc06a6","tid":197721,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T06:07:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電池位應該背面有個制 一禁就會彈舊電出黎</blockquote><br />\n家下好多同電話一樣無得拆電啦, 要拆晒螺絲甩個大身殼先換到電 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da0d135306ee28918b9eae0ed7d8fa39dc01449","tid":197721,"uid":57088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T06:09:17.000Z","msg":"唔識自己换就拎去代理换<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}